SEARCH
Package it.polimi.GC13.view.GUI.game

Interface CardManager

All Known Implementing Classes:
MainPage, OnSetLastTurnDialog, WinningFrame
public interface CardManager
Interface for managing various card-related functionalities and storing image paths in the game GUI. This interface provides constants for resource directories and image file names, as well as methods to display specific cards.

    • showStarterCardAndPrivateObjectiveCard

      void showStarterCardAndPrivateObjectiveCard(List<Integer> hand) throws IOException
      Displays the starter card and private objective card for the given hand.
      Parameters:
      hand - The list of card IDs representing the player's hand.
      Throws:
      IOException - If an I/O error occurs while displaying the cards.
